{"tid":1161826,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)風河谷謀殺案 八惡人 殺神特工","createTime":"2019-05-19T12:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T16:53:48.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"730d82d33d7aab23f3e070a771666b278bfba183","tid":1161826,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=1d03409f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=8b3c0d06\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=e607169b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a5/Wind_River_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa5%2FWind_River_Poster.jpg&h=816d4513&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/08/The_Hateful_Eight_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F08%2FThe_Hateful_Eight_Poster.jpg&h=7193da7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/98/Wanted_film_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F9%2F98%2FWanted_film_poster.jpg&h=8f65d77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述任職於美國魚類及野生動物管理局的當地獵人柯瑞&middot;藍伯特在風河谷印第安保護區的鑽探站六英哩外的荒涼雪地上發現了少女娜塔莉&middot;漢森的屍體。當FBI新人女探員珍&middot;班納前來調查時，她卻沒有對懷俄明州的寒冷天候做準備；這使得不熟悉當地的班納必須與藍伯特合作，共同深入探索這個被暴力蹂躪的未知真相<br />\n<br />\n2.故事設定於美國南北戰爭後的六年、八年或十二年左右，一輛驛馬車在正值冬天的懷俄明州的雪地中疾駛而過。車上的乘客是正要帶著通緝重犯杜黛詩前去紅石小鎮領賞金的賞金獵人尊洛夫。途中，他們遇見兩個陌生人：曾為北軍騎兵的惡名昭彰的賞金獵人華馬龍、自稱為紅石鎮新警長的孟基斯。在暴風雪中，四人躲進一間驛馬車站避難。迎接他們的不是驛站主人米妮，而是另外四張陌生面孔：臨時驛站長阿卜、紅石鎮的劊子手巫柯道、牛仔祖嘉舒和南軍將領史沙狄。隨著暴風雪席捲這座山間驛站，這八個旅人逐漸明白，他們可能永遠也到不了紅石鎮&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.在芝加哥，24歲的衛斯理（詹姆斯&middot;麥艾維飾）生活平凡，終日游手好閒，在公司工作時常被老闆責罵，女朋友又對他視若無睹，還和他的同事有一腿。因此衛斯理總是沉浸在無比的無奈與痛苦之中，生活對他來說沒有任何意義。在一次偶然的機會中，一個叫火狐狸（安潔莉娜&middot;裘莉飾）的刺客將他自一場混亂的槍戰中救出。火狐狸告訴衛斯理，與他關係一向淡薄的冷酷父親並不是多年前過世的，而是在前一天出任務時不幸遭到殺害的。火狐狸還表示，衛斯理的父親是一個刺客，隸屬於一個神秘的刺客組織&mdash;&mdash;「刺客聯盟」，這個有百年歷史的組織專門訓練擁有異能的刺客，組織成員必須誓死服從聯盟鐵律，以「刺殺一人，拯救千人」為座右銘。火狐狸之所以會找上衛斯理，是因為衛斯理身上也流著刺客的血，因此組織想全力訓練衛斯理，希望喚醒他體內潛伏的才能，讓他可以為父親復仇<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=f8d20d93\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=4eeb772e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6ff94680f7e2146a6ca8aa5411dc7474600766","tid":1161826,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f582571d894e44a270761d8709c8ed950decaf1","tid":1161826,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8d99bc8b3176935568bd64ad918016604e17d6","tid":1161826,"uid":151398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"第二套好似幾吸引"},{"pid":"d5acf9cbf8bf9704ac5d74c73ccbb1ebef89472c","tid":1161826,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43408a69f8e5949b334fa783950eaae64c9b6e5","tid":1161826,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7b9018ac4d2729061b82afe8721e40d5475730","tid":1161826,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}